<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .container {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      padding-top: 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .completion-icon {
      color: #10b981;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Document Fully Executed!</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Hello <%= @creator.name %>,</p>

    <p>Great news! Your document "<strong><%= @document.title %></strong>" has been fully executed. All signers have completed the signing process.</p>

    <p><span class="completion-icon">âœ“</span> Document completed on: <%= @document.completed_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>

    <p>You can view the fully executed document by clicking the button below:</p>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= @document_url %>" class="btn">View Document</a>
    </p>

    <p>Thank you for using DocuMarkr for your document signing needs.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email from DocuMarkr. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> DocuMarkr. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 